title: Revenue of the Oakland Raiders ( NFL ) 2001 to 2018
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Revenue in million U.S. dollars. In total the number of data points it has is 18.
In general Revenue in million U.S. dollars has rose over the Year.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2013 and 2014.
Maximum Revenue in million U.S. dollars, about 357.0 was reported at Year 2018
Minimum Revenue in million U.S. dollars about 132.0 was reached at Year 2001
